index.html:
<html><head><link href="https://cdn.syncfusion.com/ej2/28.1.33/{{theme}}.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
            body{
                touch-action:none;
            }
            .control-section{
                margin-top:100px;
            }
        </style></head><body><div class="stackblitz-container {{theme}}">
<div class="col-lg-12 control-section">
    <link href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/demos/src/diagram/styles/diagram-common.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Toolbar Icon CSS */
        @font-face {
            font-family: "e-diagram-icons";
            src: url(data:application/x-font-ttf;charset=utf-8;base64,) format("truetype");
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .e-diagram-icons {
            font-family: "e-diagram-icons";
            font-size: 54px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: normal;
            font-variant: normal;
            text-transform: none;
            line-height: 1;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        .e-diagram-reset::before {
            content: "\e715";
        }

        .e-reset::before {
            content: "\e715";
        }

        .bootstrap .e-diagram-reset::before {
            content: "\e722";
        }

        .material .e-diagram-reset::before {
            content: "\e70a";
        }


        .loading-indicator {
            border: 4px solid #f3f3f3;
            border-top: 4px solid #3498db;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
        }


        .tick {
            display: none;
            animation: showTick 0.5s 0.2s forwards;
            font-size: 10px;
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            padding-left: 4px;
            padding-top: 2.5px;
            line-height: 1;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .e-play {
            content: '\e70C';
        }

        .tick {
            background-color: green;
        }

        .cross {
            display: none;
            animation: showTick 0.5s 0.2s forwards;
            font-size: 10px;
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            padding-left: 4.5px;
            padding-top: 2.5px;
            line-height: 1;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: red;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% {
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }

            100% {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }

        @keyframes showTick {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.5);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
    </style>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div>
            <div style="width: 100%;height: 10%">
                <div id="toolbar" style="width:100%;height: 10%;margin-top: 10px;">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div id="diagram"></div>
                <div id="dialog"></div>
                <div id="endDialog"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>




<style>
</style>
</div></body></html>
